name: 小糸
text: なんか、いつもより静かだね
trans: It's like, quieter than usual, isn't it.

name: 小糸
text: テスト期間だからかな……
trans: Maybe because it's now the exam period...

name: 雛菜
text: 雛菜、いつもすぐ帰っちゃうからよくわかんないかも～
trans:
Maybe cos Hinana always leaves school right after, 
I don't know how it's usually like〜

name: 小糸
text: と、図書室で少し勉強していく？
trans: W-Wanna go study a little at the library？

name: 雛菜
text:
ん～……
でも、人いっぱいいそうだよね～……
trans:
Hm〜... Seems like there'd be a ton of people there,
though〜…

name: 雛菜
text:
あれ～、円香先輩もいる～！
何してるの～？
trans:
Hm～ Madoka-senpai's here too〜!
Whatcha guys doing〜?

name: 小糸
text: いつもはバスケ部の人たちがいるもんね……！
trans:
Well, the basketball club members are usually using
it, so...!

name: 雛菜
trans:
Aha〜
Hinana wanna do it too〜!

name: 雛菜
text:
あは～
なんか楽しいかも～

name: 円香
text:
それより寒い……
私は先に行くから
trans:
More importantly, it's cold...
I'm heading back first.

name: 教師
text: ちょっと何やってんの、こんなとこで
trans: Hey there. What are you guys doing here?

name: 教師
text: あなたたち、演劇部じゃないわよね？
trans: You're not from the drama club, right?

name: 教師
text: 発声練習でもしてるのかと思ったわよ
trans:
And here I thought you guys were doing voice
projection practice.

name: 教師
text: 遊んでないで、早く帰って勉強しなさいよ
trans: Stop playing around and hurry home to study.

name: 小糸
trans: Huh, but doesn't the drama club...

name: 円香
text:
滅相もない
帰宅部のたわむれ
trans:
Yeah, there's no way they'd do that.
It's just a guise for the going-home club.
